                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On July 3, the Department of State released a memorandum directed to the
                    authority of the President to order the Armed Forces of the United States to
                    repel the aggressive attack on the Republic of Korea; excerpts from the
                    memorandum are printed in the Department of State <hi rend="italic"
                        >Bulletin</hi>, July 31, 1950, pages 173–177, and a list of historical
                    precedents is printed <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, pages 177–178.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
